      {
        "startDie": 1,
        "endDie": 2,
        "name": "Void Ray (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Voidweaver channels the power of the void through its form, firing a beam of dark energy that deals D4+1 Arcane damage on a hit.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Cosmic Distortion (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Voidweaver manipulates the fabric of reality, creating a zone of cosmic distortion. Creatures within the room have Disadvantage on weapon Skills and Dodge checks, as the void's unpredictable energies disrupt their movements and perception. The zone lasts for 2 rounds, resetting on rolling it again.</p></div>"
