      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Void Nova (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Voidweaver harnesses the chaotic power of the void within itself, causing a violent burst of energy. All creatures within the room take D6 Arcane damage. Additionally, creatures that fail an Athletics check are pushed down to their knees, becoming Prone.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>Brought into the material plane as a result of a ritual summoning, Voidweavers are creatures attuned to the chaotic forces of the void, wielding dark astral magic in combat. Its form is an ever-shifting mass of swirling shadows and cosmic dust, a mesmerizing display of cosmic energy harnessed by its will. When provoked, the Voidweaver unleashes its formidable void magic, manipulating dark energies to distort the fabric of reality and tearing its enemies apart with powerful void rays.</p></div>",
